Dialogs.Dialog: Manaka
What's with that person？
Something about a place... Ah, look！ He's shouting！ Can you see them？
If you can see it... Can I see it too？
It's a little far... Is that okay？
Yes. Because time spent with you is important... I'm kidding. Let's go♪
Huh？ What are you doing？
Manaka
Ah, sorry. I was speaking with a friend, someone from other class.
A girl？ Do I know her？
...Geez. I'll never tell you.
(I didn't mean it like that！)
Manaka
Hey, there is a vending machine... Oden...
Yes, it's Oden. The ingredients are the correct ones.
It's not Oden-flavored juice...
Eh！？
Ah... I know that. I know there's not Oden juice, okay？ Emm... Isn't it fun？
(Oden juice... That would be extreme...)
Manaka
...Kyaa.
Uwa！
...Hmm. Hey, that girl's skirt flipped up, did you see？？
Just for a moment.
...If that were to happen to me, does that mean other could see it？
Absolutely not！
Then, you absolutely must not！ Understand？
(I will do my best...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲, right here.
Manaka
Emm... Why？
...Ah I saw ▲高嶺＊＊▲ watching the ones over there.
Is that so...？ Wasn't it your imagination？
...Hehe, yes. Thank you for protecting me.
Manaka
Is there a family restaurant over there？
It's a drink bar, how many cups can you drink？
How about this... How many you can drink, if you work part-time here.
How many？ If I was the only one, then you would run out off drinks. What would you do？
(▲高嶺＊＊▲, sometimes she's not interested...)
Manaka
Oh... a nice cafe.
It's true. Somehow I feel like I'm in France.
A place where if your whisper your love, you won't want to go home.
Je t'aime, ▲高嶺＊＊▲▼
That doesn't work here. Hehe！
Manaka
Oh, that person... Hey, recently I've been seeing people with game consoles outside...
Yes, I wonder if it's Streetpass.
Streetpass？
If you pass by someone with the same console, you can do many things. Exchange data, fight...
Amazing！ Just by passing？ Don't you need a line？
(She sounds like a granny saying that...)
Manaka
Some people are writing emails while walking, I wonder if it's not dangerous.
It's dangerous, you have to be careful about bicycles or cars――.
Ah！？
...I need to be careful too.
Yes... I was surprised...
Manaka
Ah... Did you see？ Lightning.
Rain is coming... Guerrilla heavy rain！
Emm, for real？
Let's go to the shelter！ ▲高嶺＊＊▲, your hand！
...Hehe, yes. Emm... Shall we dash？
Yes, dash！
Manaka
It's great weather, isn't it？
I'm sure ▲高嶺＊＊▲ is a sunny woman.
Then, are you a sunny man？
I wonder... actually, both of us are into rain and work with out with that？
Either way, isn't our compatibility perfect？ Hehe！
Manaka
Ah, look！ An electric bulletin board.
"I like Yukiko！" Oh, a confession！ I wonder if I should make it that way, would you be glad？
That is... a no.
Hmm？
I'm happy when you tell me directly... so... Right？
Manaka
Hmm？
Kyaa！
I'm... I'm sorry. I was... Geez, no.
(It's certainly embarrassing if you do it yourself...)
Manaka
It seems celebrities come often to that ramen shop.
Celebrities. Do you know any ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
That's a way to say it. I don't know any.
I see, sorry. Then what kind of persons？
...I forgot. That's the end of the story.
(I should stop pushing further...)
Manaka
Ah, did you see？ A fashion couple.
It's true. I wonder if they feel good doing it together.
Is there any way to research it？ I wonder if I'm enough as I'm now...
Me too, I wonder if I'm enough to be with you...
Don't say it like that. Geez.
Manaka
Rain...？
Ah, certainly. It's a fox marriage.
Then, I will say yes... I'm kidding.
Hmm？ You're kidding right？
...Geez.
Manaka
Ah. Hey, the song I just heard...
Hmm？ What's going on？
Didn't you hear it？ Emm... it was a song.
How？ If you sing it, I may understand.
You know... I forgot about it. Will I hear it again？ I'm interested.
(I'm also interested！)
Manaka
Ah, I kicked a rock.
Pass！
Emm... Emm, pass...？
Nice assist！
Gool！ Alright, a hug as a reward！
I won't do it. Hehehe！
Manaka
Hey, can you look at the upper wall of that building？
Hmm？... What？ That door？
It says "Emergency Exit", but there are no stairs... Isn't it strange？
Not really. More importantly, why is there and emergency exit sign on the outside.
Yes... it's weird... A little scary, right？ I wonder why...
(▲高嶺＊＊▲, that something might fright you is rare...)
Manaka
Hey, he's giving out tissues, you got any？
Of course. Didn't you get any, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yes... I was distracted and I got so nervous...
I will give you courage next time.
(Courage... I wonder if it's necessary.)
Manaka
Hey, at the top of that building. Is there a person over there？
Hmm. It looks like it, how can you see it？
Hmm, you can't see well...
With such a defenseless face, I could prank you！
Emm？ I don't make that kind of face... Geez.
Manaka
Ah, a large puddle.
If you have boots, you can jump in them！
Yes, go ahead. I'll take a look at you▼
Yup. I'll go for it！
Emm... Sorry, I meant it as a joke...！
Haha, I know！
Ah... Geez！
Manaka
The parasol of the people walking if front of us is wonderful.
It's just a parasol... Boys don't get into that kind of thing.
Is that right？ Then, I'll give you one as a present.
Eh！ A parasol... for me！？
Hehe. Because you think it's cute, right？
No, no！
Manaka
We passed near a baby recently, wasn't he cute？
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Did you make him laugh？ Making faces, or the like.
Yes, it was nice... Hey, do you like babies？
Hmm？ Well, I suppose.
I'm glad♪
Manaka
Hey, do you know that kind of small tree？
The one with the little red fruit？
Yes. I've always been interested, and I think about looking it up, but I forget when I get home.
Haha, that happens. I'm sure you'll forget about it and ask again.
That happens！ I'm kidding.
Manaka
I wish I could see that cloud shape again...
Cloud shape？
Yes. Do you know they change depending on the season？
I see. Then, next year we'll try to look for it.
It will be done. I'm kidding, Hehe！
Manaka
Ah, a bookstore.
Hmm？ Want to stop by？
Emm... Yes, is that okay right now？
Haha, what was that voice. Okay, let's enter the bookstore.
I wonder why I made that voice. Emm... Tehe♪
Manaka
Hey, umm... a lump？ What is that？
Ah, that's... some kind of object.
I wonder about that. But, nobody is watching it.
Right. Even though it has a strong presence.
Yes, then let's see it ourselves, right？
(I'm watching...)
Manaka
There's an empty space over there, isn't it？
Oh, it says it's looking for tenants.
I heard rumors there could be a Winning Burger build there, do you think it's true？
I wonder about that... It's because that's small, right？
That's right. It needs to be a wide space like in the station...
(I'm curious about it...)
Manaka
A doll swinging its arms in the middle of a construction...
Hmm？ Is it scary？
...Why does it look like you're having fun？
It's a boyfriend's duty to protect his scared girlfriend！
But that's not what it means... Geez, but it's fine nonetheless.
Manaka
Ah, a maid.
She's handing off leaflets. Is it for a maid cafe？ But ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Yes, over there.
See you, I'm trying to embarrass you by doing this.
(I'm already embarrassed.)
Manaka
...Hey, the shape of that plane is strange, isn't it？
Hmm. Certainly... it looks like a car.
I saw news that another country was developing a flying car... It can't be, right？
No way！ I'm not sure because it's still far away, but it's an airship.
Yes...
(...Is that right？)
Manaka
There are lots of pigeons on the wire...
True. We're passing under！
Really？ It's cute. Is it over there？
Not there！ Over there...
Ah... Yes, I can see it from the distance.
Manaka
The pedestrian bridge over there is not used much.
There's a pedestrian crossing next to it.
Yes... I haven't used it, it might be rusty.
Maybe... Okay, let's cross it！
Hehe, yes.
Manaka
"Take you time"
Hmm？ Ah, that traffic slogan. It was made by elementary school students.
Well then, you can do it too. Yes.
Huh！ “I think Manaka Takane is cute！” Yes！
...That's not a slogan... Geez.
Manaka
Ah, what a cute taxi.
Where？ I mean... a cute taxi？
Yes. Lots of stuffed animals. Also, it's decorated with lace.
I wonder if it's of a female driver.
It was from a grandpa. Isn't it cute？
(...Really？)
Manaka
Ah！？
Hmm？ What's wrong？
Right now I saw... a very big rat...
Ah, a big brown rat.
No, it was more like... a big dog.
A dog-sized mouse！？
I made a mistake... but...
(Towano City first ever dog-sized mouse...)
Manaka
Wow... Is that a classic car？ That's my kind of car.
Oh, that's cool. However, maintenance seems to be difficult.
I would like it, even if it's difficult.
I sure hope you understand what you're saying ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
...That's wrong. I hate people without delicacy.
(She's angry. Understanding women is difficult...)
Manaka
Ah！.. No.
Huh？ What？
A doll is standing over there... I thought it was a person...
(It's uncle Carneore... You don't know him？)
Manaka
Ah, there's a small bento shop over there.
It's true. I'll buy one next time.
...Don't.
Why？
It's my job to do that... What do you say？
Yes.
Manaka
Hmm？
Rock, paper... scissors.
Ah！！
You devil▼ Oni-chan！
Oh, that's unfair！
Manaka
Hey, there are games over there, even though it's a candy store？
It's the game corner of the candy shop. It's a fighting game.
Fighting... Hmm.
Interested？ Do you think you can find someone stronger than me？
Geez, was that an imitation？ Hehe.
Manaka
...Hey, there are people standing there, right？
Maybe some kind of performance. They paint their whole body... that looks painful.
Yes... Your skin can't breathe through the paint, so it's going to be unpleasant.
It's art from the soul... It's brilliant！
Geez, what？ That's... Hehehe！
Manaka
Wow, those clothes are cute▼
Yes, they look great！ Try them！
Emm... is that okay？ Taking a detour...
Yes, sensei！ I think a detour in a date is good！
...Hehe！ I'm just going to try them, I won't stay long, I'm kidding.
Manaka
...No！ Hehe！
What？
That signboard... Ramen...？
Ramen... It's true！ I didn't notice... I should have seen it before.
Rameen... Hehehe, no more.
Manaka
I wonder if it's going to be sunny tomorrow...
Tomorrow？ Why？
I want to hang my futon. I couldn't dry it today.
I see, I forgot to dry it too.
A fluffy futon feels good, right？ I wonder if you need my help.
It's okay, I can do it myself！
Manaka
Can you say the order of the traffic light colors, looking at the sky？
Eh. from the left...
From the left？
...Yellow in the middle！
Correct！.. Geez. Hehe！
Manaka
Hey, what's that strange vehicle？
Ah, that's a stand-up motorcycle. It seems to be popular overseas.
Hmm... Sounds nice and funny. I want to ride it.
It would be better to ride it together！
Hehe, yes. Should I look into it later？
Manaka
I wonder how Ueki can craft such beautiful things.
Hmm？ Ah, the garden over there.
It seems impossible for me to make it so flat.
Oh, this one looks expensive. Hmm？ This one too...
Hehe, yes, it's gone, I'm going to do it too.
Manaka
Hmm？
That person's clothes...
Oh！ They are the same as mine's.
Yes, it seems like that.
(It's somehow awkward...)
Manaka
Hey, have you ever walked along the white line on the sidewalk？
Only your feet can touch the white line！ Like that？
Yes yes. Aren't child masters on creating games？
That's right... Ah, that face...
Hehe, correct. Don't fall until you reach your destination, okay？ Okay, start！
Manaka
Isn't that barber's pole strange？
Strange？ The origin of that color has various theories around it, you know？
Yes. But why did it had to be a spiral？ Always turning around...
(I'm interested in it. ▲高嶺＊＊▲ thinks unusual things sometimes.)
Manaka
Ah！ The smell of a bakery.
Really. This smell makes me hungry. It's unfair！
Maybe it's promotion？ Emm... You know, a sales promotion.
Ah！！ A pun... Did you make a pun ▲高嶺＊＊▲！？
...Why do you have to act so surprised？ Geez.
Manaka
Danger！ A bee！
Emm, where！？
On your shoulder... Ah, I said it. I'm sorry, I was surprised.
It fine. More than that, I'm glad it didn't go towards you ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
...Geez. I was just worried. Won't you do the same for me？
Manaka
If we walked without being aware of each other... Is there a difference in speed？
I wonder. Probably we have different strides.
Is that right？...
Hmm？
You're so kind, after all. Hehe！
(Don't be shy if you say it...)
Manaka
Ah. Sticky insects.
Truly... Huh, is that a sticky insect？ or a catchy insect？
You mean Onami？ I wonder if it's called differently... I have to look it up.
(▲高嶺＊＊▲ really likes to research things.)
Manaka
You may have heard about replacing the dust paper after a long time.
Certainly. I heard about it when I was little.
Not many people use the word "dust paper", right？ Are there other words like that？
Emm... Like Monkake？ My relatives said something like that.
Monkake！ Hey, are there some more word？
(▲高嶺＊＊▲'s curiosity is ignited...)
Manaka
The people we just passed by were humming and singing.
Seriously？ I didn't notice...
You are good at it, aren't you？
Haha！ I can't do humming at that level.
Maybe. Hehe！
Manaka
That girl playing over there is good at skipping.
Ah, it's true. Can you also skip ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
...I can, you know？ With an unique rhythm.
An unique rhythm...？ You know, right here――.
...If you skip in such a place, won't it be a bother？ Look, I'm going now.
(I'm sorry...)
Manaka
Ah, it's sprinkling water.
It's true. It seems like sprinkling water is not only in summer.
Yes. It seems it's used to settle dust from the ground.
I see.
I used to do this at home. How many years since then, I wonder？
Manaka
There's a game similar to rock, paper and scissors, isn't there？
Yes, I did it when I was a kid？
Yes... If you do it now, you'll be embarrassed, right？
There's no such word in an idiot couple's dictionary！
Geez, an idiot couple... Yes, that's right, isn't it？ Then, rock...
(Scissors！)
Manaka
Hey, in rock, paper why do we say "rock"？
That was sudden. Maybe paper stands for "paper roll".
Then, what about "rock"？
"Rock n'roll！" Maybe.
Hehe, really？ Then in "rock,paper, scissors", what does scissors mean？
(This is really funny...)
Manaka
I think sparrows are rarely seen these days, don't you？
It seems their numbers are decreasing.
That so... Ah, I want to see one... they are cute.
I hope the cause can be reverted.
Yes...
Manaka
Why is that pigeon so calm？
Even if humans come near, they don't fly... If you run, they just calmly walk.
You mean, do they think don't think of us as humans？
Haha, probably！ Like, you should walk near the edge！
So we say "I'm sorry Pigeon-san" I'm kidding. Hehe！
Manaka
Ah... My eye...
Are you okay？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲, it's easy to hurt your eyes.
Really...？ I wonder if I should walk with my eyes closed.
(That's dangerous...)
Manaka
Ah！？
Hmm？ What happened？
I wonder... Is that a spiderweb？
Are you okay？
Yes. But I broke their nest.
You didn't do it with any ill will, it can't be helped.
You have to be careful. Perhaps we were so focused on our chat.
Manaka
？ Hey, what does that sign means？
Hmm？... Certainly, it's rare.
A deer mark... You don't see one here, right？
Did they put it wrong？ Or, have deer actually appeared？
Wouldn't it be great？ We could have fun. Hehe！
Manaka
That sound...
A pistol？ I wonder if there's an event somewhere.
Do you think some competition started nearby？
Right. Then if it sounds next time, let's race！
Hehe, I can't lose.
(▲高嶺＊＊▲, really？ I can't win against you.)
Manaka
Ah. First yellow car.
What's that？ Finding 100 objects around？
That's right. Do you think I can find it today？
Even if you don't find it, happiness is in front of ▲高嶺＊＊▲... Look！
...Yes, that's right？ Hehehe！
(That's good...)
Manaka
Wow, a rainbow...！
Truly. But it's not raining... Then why？
Yes, it's strange.
By our power, we can make miracles happen！
Hehe！ Then I hope there are many more in the future, right？
Manaka
Ah, a soap bubble.
Ah, a child is over there. So innocent.
Don't this make you wanna sing？
Go ahead！
I should not. Next time, right？
(Tsk.)
Manaka
That boy last time, did he speak in English？
He was. And he is so small...
His mother seems to be Japanese, maybe he is half-blood？
That's right. It might be cool for a child to speak English. Maybe our children will do that too？
...Geez, it's unfair to say that unconsciously.
Manaka
Ah！？
Hah... It seems like I bumped into something.
Hmm？ Was it scary？
No, but thank you for always worrying about me.
Manaka
Ah.
Hmm？
Look, look. There's something over there...
Eh, where？
A secret. A secret only for myself. I'm kidding.
Manaka
Huh？ What？
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you have long eyelashes.
Really？... But why are you telling me that.
How much can I say？ Your eyes are big and cute, your skin is beautiful and...
No！.. Geez.
(But it's true！)
Manaka
Kyaa！
Huh！？ What happened？
Right now, my back... Did you touch it？
Me？ I didn't do it, okay？
Emm... Then... Who...？
...I'm sorry. It was me.
Geez！
Manaka
Passing in front of the cake shop, makes me wanna enter...
Can't you make them yourself？
Of course. If you can, you should make them yourself, but you can't beat the store's flavor.
Is that right？
Yes. But I'm glad you say that.
Manaka
When I walked this way... There are various types of nameplates.
There are. Wood, stone, metal...
What do you want to use？
Hmm？
I'm talking to myself！
Manaka
Look, look. A round post.
Ah, yes. I noticed it recently.
Yes, I didn't notice. I like more the square post.
Is it cute？
Yes▼ In the olden days, there was a piggy bank back in my house... I should ask it it's there.
Manaka
Did you see the number of the car we just passed？
I didn't see it. Was it a rare number？
I was the same as your birthday.
Eh！ It would be nice to have seen it！
I would be glad if you had noticed it sooner, okay？
(I wonder if a car with her birthday will pass.)
Manaka
Hey, there's a vending machine here... but why does it have a 4 digits display？
Oh, when the four digits are the same, you'll get an extra from the machine.
Emm, it's amazing.
It's rare, though.
It's a great vending machine... But, I wonder if I can drink them both.
(Well, that will happen until it hits 4 digits...)
Manaka
I like passing by the flower shop.
Because it smells good？
There is that too, but I feel fresh when going inside.
You get power from the flowers.
Yes▼ Let's buy something and go home.
Manaka
Some people are walking while eating croquettes...
Oh, there seems to be a butcher in this neighborhood that sells freshly fried croquettes.
Hmm...
Do you want to stop by？ We're near anyway！
Yes... I'm curious... But...
(I feel it would be a bother to eat while walking...)
Manaka
The streelights in Towano City are often cute, right？
Heh？ Ah, truly...
Hehe！ I wonder if boys don't really care about cute things, don't you？
For that, I can trust you to decide, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Yay, I was trusted▼ I'm kidding.
Manaka
Why are am I being asked for directions today？
Maybe because of your "nice person aura"？
Hehe, what's that... But it's easy to talk because we often laugh when we're together.
I see... Yes, it may be that.
Right？ I hope we can always be like this.
Manaka
Ah, balloons.
Something on the end of the string... Is that a letter？
I hope it will be carried far away, and both of them have a good relationship.
Well then, let's send one together！
Yes. Hehe！
Manaka
Huh！？ That public telephone is ringing...
It seems like it's somewhere near...
Hey, should I answer it？
I'm sure it's a mistake or something. Otherwise, isn't it scary？
Huh？ Why？ I was surprised...
(Sorry...)
Manaka
There aren't many people or cars today, right？
Whether it's a drama or a movie like this, people are gone from all over the world.
Then, are we now the last two people in the world.
Alright... ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
That's too bad！
Manaka
Wow, that's a very big shoe... a sign, maybe？
▲高嶺＊＊▲, it seems we can go inside.
Yes. In fact, if I was that size, I wonder how tall I would be.
Hmm... Maybe around １００ｍ？
Can you imagine something like that？ I want to experience that view.
Manaka
That postman's red bike it's cute.
Cute？ Not cool？
Yeah, cute, when I was in elementary school, I wanted to ride one.
Riding a motorcycle is quickly for us ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Would I look good？ I'm kidding.
(I might want to look at you...？)
Manaka
Ah, a mover... a moving store, isn't it？
Yes. That large bag requires a lot of people to carry it.
...When I move, would I require less people？
Eh, are you moving？
No, in the future.
Manaka
Ah, a doggy.
Huh？ Does it have an owner？
Yes... Ah. Its stopping at the pedestrian crosswalk.
A dog that takes a walk at will...
That kind of dog it's amazing.
Manaka
A courier is always running, isn't it？
Certainly, they do have that image, and I saw it earlier.
Is that a rule？
I don't think it's like that... I hope？
He seems to be physically strong, right？ Should I try that voluntary work in my training？
(How you would do that？)
Manaka
Hey, that car was being moved by a tow truck...
Yes yes.
It might have been Papa's car.
Huh... Eh！
It might have been a mistake because it was just a moment. I don't know...
(If so, that would be tough...)
Manaka
Ah... Hey, the person around the corner now... didn't she look like me？
Her clothes are the same, aren't they？
No. It's like me when I become an adult...
Huh！ Where！ I'll go after you！
(She got jealous...)
Manaka
Hey, have you been to a public bath？
And you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
No, so I thought I'd like to go there once.
Then, today, just the two of us--！
It sounds interesting, but... I'm sure Mama and Papa would be surprised. Forgive me for asking.
Manaka
Someone is washing their hair at the barber... I wonder why they wash it facing down.
Ah, I see. The beauty salon is on the back.
Does your face gets splashed with hot water？
I can't recommend it to women who are wearing makeup.
Hmm... It might be funny.
(Do you want to go？)
Manaka
Huh？ Did something shine just now？
Hmm？ Oh, really. It's like a Morse code... What's the sign？
How should I study Morse code？
(Are you also interested in that...？)
Manaka
Ah, contrails.
They remain for a long time without erasing, which means that the weather is downhill.
Really？
It's because the sky is damp！.. I just saw something.
That's right. Then I'll go tell someone else what you told me.
Manaka
The girl who just waved from the bus, wasn't she cute？
When I looked back, I waved back.
Yes. I really understand how you feel, it's fun to look back.
Yay, ▲高嶺＊＊▲ー▼
Yay▼ Hehehe！
